{"tid":926981,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"睇到世一摩迷講中場同前鋒比數據點比,真係好嘔心","createTime":"2018-12-04T00:14:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T08:39:07.000Z","uid":25345,"like":32,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"98691202c77e165db42cc275aa909198c0e75f14","tid":926981,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T00:14:13.000Z","msg":"fine<br />\n冇得咁比,咁球隊成績呢,牙朗,美斯<br />\n唔好話佢地數據唔好,就算球隊輸波和波都入哂佢地數<br />\n一唔贏就屌到仆街,點解世一摩可以置身事外咁,和波輸波<br />\n我係中場喎,關我撚事咁<br />\n輸到咁款都好似唔關佢事,咁佢仲講咩carry全隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算係中場,數據邊有人有佢咁差?<br />\n點計佢都算攻中啦,入波助攻創造威脅?<br />\n施丹都係攻中,數據都係佢幾倍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入波幾球,助攻幾球,咩攻中咁勁抽呀carry全隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勤力?牛夠勤力啦,唔好比簡迪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f13f6e0167671df6a5caf53c971a0021b5c2a51","tid":926981,"uid":311,"like":22,"dislike":4,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T00:22:43.000Z","msg":"摩迪係攻中都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d69e0129ea79bb2ebe7ea719684075ae863ef3b","tid":926981,"uid":2419,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T00:30:50.000Z","msg":"唔係撐摩迪<br />\n不過笑左 摩迪係攻中<br />\n睇多幾年波先死出黎9up啦屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0927cc3c740815310b7444ce2c44a574cd1df233","tid":926981,"uid":3194,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T04:42:16.000Z","msg":"如果淨係同基沙文包皮果啲比, 佢係值得拎, 依家要同兩大球皇比, 點都唔值啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla